TY  - JOUR
T1  - Ideology and Performance in Public Organizations
AU  - Spenkuch, Jörg L.
AU  - Teso, Edoardo
AU  - Xu, Guo
Y1  - 2023/07/01
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2023/07/01
